description:
I went shopping at Rainbow Grocery Coop in San Francisco to show you my top 12 vegan food basics that I use in my cooking and snacking. This episode especially goes to those who are still new to the plant based lifestyle. But if you are already an OG in the vegan world, please DO share what are your top vegan food basics as well as tips and techniques you'd like to share with us!

Thanks for watching!

For more information about Rainbow Grocery Coop
http://www.facebook.com/rainbowgrocery
